        <heading>Penalties</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 71-1203. Penalties.\n  Any person who violates the provisions of article twenty-two of this\nchapter shall be subject to a civil penalty not to exceed ten thousand\ndollars for each day during which such violation occurred; provided,\nhowever, that the total penalty to be imposed shall not exceed one\nmillion dollars.\n</p>
